This MIT license covers the source code of videokit (SKILL.md, reference/, scripts/, assets/templates and LUTs, etc.).

Third-party models downloaded at runtime by `scripts/download-assets.ps1` and `scripts/smart-reframe.py` retain their own licenses:

- RNNoise `cb.rnnn` — Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY 4.0). Source: https://github.com/GregorR/rnnoise-models
- MediaPipe BlazeFace `blaze_face_short_range.tflite` — Apache License 2.0. Source: Google MediaPipe (https://github.com/google-ai-edge/mediapipe).

These model files are NOT redistributed by this repository. They are downloaded on demand from official upstream sources and stored locally in `assets/audio-models/` and `assets/face-detector/` (both gitignored).
